'''氰化亚硝酰'''是一种化合物，化学式为ONCN，它是蓝绿色气体。<ref name=Kirby>{{cite journal |doi=10.1039/CS9770600001|title=Tilden Lecture. Electrophilic C-nitroso-compounds|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_chemical-society-great-britain-chemical-society-reviews_1977_6_1/page/n4|year=1977|last1=Kirby|first1=G. W.|journal=Chemical Society Reviews|volume=6|page=1}}</ref>它是葡萄糖氧化酶催化的[[氨基氰|氨基氰]]氧化的产物。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/0006-2952(96)00174-8|title=Nitrosyl cyanide, a putative metabolic oxidation product of the alcohol-deterrent agent cyanamide|year=1996|last1=Shirota|first1=Frances N.|last2=Goon|first2=David J.W.|last3=Demaster|first3=Eugene G.|last4=Nagasawa|first4=Herbert T.|journal=Biochemical Pharmacology|volume=52|issue=1|pages=141–147|pmid=8678898}}</ref>  

==制备与结构==
氰化亚硝酰可由[[亚硝酰氯|亚硝酰氯]]和[[氰化银|氰化银]]在低温反应得到，它是平面分子，结构类似于[[亚硝酰氯|亚硝酰氯]]。<ref name=Kirby/>计算表明它可能存在同分异构体。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition in English|volume=36|issue=16|language=en|issn=0570-0833|date=1997-09-01|pages=1707–1709|doi=10.1002/anie.199717071|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/anie.199717071|title=Isomers of the Elemental Composition CN2O|accessdate=2020-07-17|author=Günther Maier, Hans Peter Reisenauer, Jürgen Eckwert, Matthias Naumann, Michael De Marco}}</ref>

